Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.28,0:23:27.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,無趣之夜
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.35,0:23:30.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓理樹君當一晚上玩具陪我們玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.08,0:23:33.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.21,0:23:35.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住…住手啦 來谷同學
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.97,0:23:37.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,任務開始
